        "richtext_cBJfQ8": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>If there is something you're not satisfied with in your order you can make a return or exchange within 30 days! Our customer service team is happy to help in any way we can. We can offer either a refund, exchange or store credit depending on your case. Please read the following information before you make your return.</p><h4><strong>RETURN EXCLUSIONS</strong></h4><p>We cannot accept final sale Items, underwear, bodysuits, wigs, swimwear, contact lenses, face masks, hosiery, jewellery, cosmetics and opened hair dye, due to Australian health & hygiene regulations. Please note we follow all ACCC requirements & refunds/exchanges will be given on all faulty items not already stated in the description. Gift cards & YouPay Orders cannot be returned and are not redeemable for cash. <br/><br/><strong>Exchanges are only available in person. </strong>You can make an exchange if your item meets the above criteria and if you are able to return the item in person to our warehouse in Virginia QLD.</p><h4><strong>FAULTY ITEMS</strong></h4><p>Please <strong>DO NOT </strong>submit it through our Returns process, but instead email us directly at: <strong>orders@beserk.com.au</strong> with a photo of the item so we can arrange a solution for you right away. This also applies to faults on FINAL SALE Items.<br/><br/><strong>Please see the full Terms And Conditions below.</strong></p>"
          }
