            "title": "Australian return",
            "content": "<h3>AUSTRALIAN RETURN</h3><p>For returns within Australia, we suggest using our Return Label service. For a Flat Rate of $10.95 you can return anything from around Australia, fully tracked. Simply click <a href=\"https://return.auspost.com.au/BESERK\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Returns Portal\"><strong>HERE</strong></a>, enter your order details and make a payment. This will then generate your return label that can be printed in the post office or at home.<br/><br/>Download and print our Return Form <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0836/9167/files/BESERK_RETURNS_FORM_2026.pdf?v=1769061212\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beserk Return Form 2026\"><strong>HERE</strong></a> or if you don't have a printer, please include a note with the following details:<br/><br/><strong>FULL NAME<br/>REASON FOR RETURN<br/>ORDER NUMBER</strong> [IF AVAILABLE]<br/><strong>CONTACT </strong>[PHONE NUMBER and EMAIL]<strong><br/>REFUND TYPE </strong>[STORE CREDIT or REFUND]</p><p>Please include clear instructions with your return. <strong>Any returns received without instructions will be processed as a store credit</strong>.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "open_on_mobile": false
          }
        },
