          "name": "International return",
          "settings": {
            "title": "International return",
            "content": "<h3>INTERNATIONAL RETURN</h3><p>Returns from outside of Australia can be made by going to your local post office and sending the product(s) back to us. Please ship it to our address and include notes about your return.</p><h4>BESERK ADDRESS</h4><p><strong>BESERK RETURNS<br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia QLD 4014 AUSTRALIA</strong></p><p>Download and print our Return Form <a href=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0836/9167/files/BESERK_RETURNS_FORM_2026.pdf?v=1769061212\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beserk Return Form 2026\"><strong>HERE</strong></a> or if you don't have a printer, please include a note with the following details:<br/><br/><strong>FULL NAME<br/>REASON FOR RETURN<br/>ORDER NUMBER</strong> [IF AVAILABLE]<br/><strong>CONTACT </strong>[PHONE NUMBER and EMAIL]<strong><br/>REFUND TYPE </strong>[STORE CREDIT or REFUND]</p><p>Please include clear instructions with your return. <strong>Any returns received without instructions will be processed as a store credit</strong>.</p>",
