            "content": "<h3>WAREHOUSE RETURNS AND EXCHANGES</h3><p>If you'd like to return or exchange your item for a different size, simply drop by the Beserk Warehouse:<br/><strong><br/>2/58 Yarraman Place,<br/>Virginia QLD 4014 AUSTRALIA</strong></p><p>Please have your order number ready and let our friendly customer service team know what size you'd like to swap for! Feel free to <a href=\"/pages/contact-us\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Contact Us\"><strong>CONTACT US</strong></a> beforehand if you'd like us to put the size aside for you so it doesn't sell out. </p>",
